The Scarlett is an adorable, dainty flower that measures approximately 1 inch. The flower is attached to a skinny, brown, elastic headband.  It will be customized to the size of your choice.  You can choose a red or brown, faux pearl center--just let us know at checkout!  


**Colors may vary slightly due to differences in monitors and lighting.
**Always supervise children wearing headbands, as they may contain small parts.

name: The Valentina
description:
The Valentina is the perfect posh accessory!  Classic girly colors--pink and white--create this posh piece!  Chic flowers, vintage-style embellishments with pearls and sparkle, as well as Nagorie feathers are used in The Valentina.  
Please select your desired size of the white, lace headband upon checkout.

**Colors may vary slightly due to differences in lighting and monitors.
**Always supervise children wearing headbands, as they may contain small parts.

name: The Rianna
description:
The Rianna is a sweet and sassy, velvety flower with glittered edges and a faux pearl center.  Complementing cream, tan, and hot pink speckled feathers fall behind it on a tan, lace headband.  

**Lace discontinued, but a comparable one will be used.

**Colors may vary slightly due to differences in monitors and lighting.

**Always supervise children wearing headbands, as they may contain small parts.

name: The Alina
description:
The Alina is a combination of femininity and vintage elegance.  Pink and black Nagorie feathers are adorned with a pink gemstone and black birdcage netting.  The Alina is attached to a thin, black, lace headband.  This is a must have for any diva or princess!

**THE PINK RHINESTONE WILL BE THE ONE IN THE FIRST PICTURE.

**Colors may vary slightly due to differences in monitors and lighting.

**Always supervise children wearing headbands, as they may contain small parts.

name: The Paris
description:
The Paris is a dual flower combination in mocha and ivory.  The two chic flowers are embellished with a cream bow and rhinestone flower.  A vintage, tan, lace headband completes the look.  

**This is also available in other colors--just ask!

**Colors may vary slightly due to differences in lighting and monitors.

**Always supervise children wearing headbands, as they may contain small parts.

name: The Delila
description:

**Always supervise children wearing headbands, as they may contain small parts.

name: Electric
description:
Electric is a royal blue, satin, fluffy flower with white and blue specked feathers.  It is attached to a shimmery, white, elastic headband that will fit infants to adults (not the lace one in the child's photo but the one in the product photo).  The flower itself has a pin and a clip, so it is completely versatile and interchangeable.  

This is a great item to match an outfit or to show support for the Indianapolis Colts (or many other teams)!  

**Colors may vary slightly due to differences in monitors and lighting.  

**Always supervise children wearing headbands, as they may contain small parts.

name: Monogram Memories Clip
description:
Monogram Memories is a fluffy satin flower designed for the special girls in your life.  It has a clip and pin on the back, so it is completely versatile.
If you prefer it as a headband, please select that item instead. 

Whichever you choose, just choose the first letter of her name at checkout!  The antique silver letter will be decorated with a pearl or rhinestone.  Please let us know if you do have a preference.

**Colors may vary slightly due to differences in monitors and lighting.

**Always supervise children wearing headbands, as they may contain small parts.

name: Monogram Memories Headband
description:
Monogram Memories is a fluffy satin flower designed for the special girls in your life.  It has a clip and pin on the back, so it is completely versatile.

The headband will be a matching lace color unless you'd like another choice.  If you prefer it as a non-slip clip, please select that item instead. 

Whichever you choose, just choose the first letter of her name at checkout!  The antique silver letter will be decorated with a pearl or rhinestone.  Please let us know if you do have a preference.

The bottoms are also patterned with zebra print.
